description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and Sean Wagner-McGough fire up an emergency podcast to react to the Jaguars trading Jalen Ramsey to the Rams. The guys discuss who won the deal, how recent games played a part in making this happen, the motivation behind moving on from Marcus Peters, deeper concerns with Los Angeles, when Ramsey could ink a new deal, and what other teams should have gotten more involved in the sweepstakes.
